heading: Faceless Shrine Dungeon Guide
content: Faceless Shrine does not contain any dangerous monsters, and has a compact, linear layout that requires some backtracking. It is solid for farming, and is currently a possible . Mother's Judgement is a boss that deals a high amount of lightning damage, but is otherwise simple to defeat. This dungeon unlocks the , a solid aspect for a Summoner Necromancer. While every dungeon has a somewhat randomized layout, there are patterns to where objectives and bosses are located. This map will help you identify those layouts so you can complete dungeons faster and maximize your XP and loot per hour! Reviewed by
